{"tid":927152,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"班死熱狗原來扔埋蕉 仲有咩係做唔出架佢地","createTime":"2018-12-04T03:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T08:49:52.000Z","uid":27485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"763b11ab7e31dd87ed03a61190b8fba3866251f9","tid":927152,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=woWKBtP6PCnvw6rWWJT%2B2jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=967aea6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】周日阿仙奴主場對熱刺的北倫敦打吡，發生客隊球迷向兵工廠射手奧巴美揚扔蕉皮的不愉快事件，阿仙奴領隊艾美利與英格蘭主帥修夫基先後開腔譴責此事。<br />\n<br />\n「我絕不會接受這種行為。沒有人會接受這種行為。我相信警方已採取行動。」艾美尼（Unai Emery）說。向黑人球員扔香蕉含有種族歧視意味，警方已拘捕肇事球迷並落案起訴他，同場另有3名球迷因其他不當行為而被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n當時Auba射入12碼為阿仙奴先開紀錄，正興高采烈跟隊友慶祝，冷不防有球迷從看台上丟下蕉皮。熱刺表示已將掟蕉者列入黑名單，無限期不得入場睇波。<br />\n<br />\n修夫基亦說：「假如事件涉及種族歧視，那絕對不可容忍。我們不斷說英國在應付種族歧視問題上日益進步，卻偏偏發生這種事，難免令人不安與關注。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n球員到球迷都係一班食屎狗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69461a45e5ab7727fb58013fc3b8bba84552309","tid":927152,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:40:22.000Z","msg":"好撚賤 自己隊都有幾個黑人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a18d33fcc401889d7af970c02f4aa4a76ec7d0","tid":927152,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"1.<br />\n2.<br />\n3.<br />\n4."},{"pid":"3c4abe712c231e38d5784c03c3cec029c6fcf207","tid":927152,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00a18d33fcc401889d7af970c02f4aa4a76ec7d0","tid":927152,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"1.<br />\n2.<br />\n3.<br />\n4."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:48:53.000Z","msg":"講一講又好似真係唔應該咁衝動怪佢地"},{"pid":"f571f868b8f3cc6d9d6a4464634fb0b97fa23c46","tid":927152,"uid":37297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"嬴波"},{"pid":"8e2fab5b9be31a34866c4b7c7ae8b0bd28d24e74","tid":927152,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T08:49:52.000Z","msg":"用歷史串人"}]}